TEMPLATE energy
SOURCE FIELDS
    REQUIRED description
END SOURCE FIELDS
ITEM FIELDS
    REQUIRED quote
    REQUIRED BUNDLE note, chain
    OPTIONAL code
END ITEM FIELDS
ONTOLOGY FIELDS
    REQUIRED description
    OPTIONAL topic
END ONTOLOGY FIELDS
FIELD description TYPE TEXT SCOPE SOURCE
END FIELD
FIELD quote TYPE QUOTATION SCOPE ITEM
END FIELD
FIELD note TYPE MEMO SCOPE ITEM
END FIELD
FIELD chain TYPE CHAIN SCOPE ITEM
    RELATIONS
        INFLUENCES: influences
        ENABLES: enables
    END RELATIONS
    ARITY >= 2
END FIELD
FIELD code TYPE CODE SCOPE ITEM
END FIELD
FIELD topic TYPE TOPIC SCOPE ONTOLOGY
END FIELD
